data.description:
You really have to see this one to truly appreciate all the upgrades given to this home. The owners did not go cheap or cut corners on the remodel!
The kitchen is open and spacious and features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and plenty of cabinet space. The living and dining room provide a great space for entertaining and create a welcoming atmosphere.
All four bedrooms are generous in size with large windows that provide plenty of natural light and ample closet space.
The windows throughout the home are custom and double hung, along with screens that slide for easy outdoor access and make cleaning a breeze. The ''hurricane proof'' patio withstood Hurricane Michael and still looks new!
Imagine coming home to a stunningly landscaped yard that just invites you in! And when you need some downtime after a long day, you can step out to an even larger backyard that's perfect for relaxing and entertaining friends and family. It's all set up and ready to go whenever you are!
-Stove and microwave replaced in 2018-Samsung Refrigerator replaced in 2022-Water Heater replaced in 2019-A/C, floors and Bathrooms remodeled in 2021-Solar Panels installed 2022-Dishwasher 2023
